    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "it's just so exhausting. the constant loop in my head of everything i ruined. sometimes i look at the empty office and think it would have been easier if none of this ever happened. if i just didn't have to deal with the shame or the debt or the look on everyone's faces. do you think anyone actually recovers from something this big? or is the damage just permanent?",
